  <text>
      <body>
        
     
      <div xml:id="Harlem"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="free"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="society"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>What happens to a dream deferred?</l>
               <l>Does it dry up</l>
               <l>like a raisin in the sun?</l>
               <l>Or fester like a sore--</l>
               <l>And then run?</l>
               <l>Does it stink like rotten meat?</l>
               <l>Or crust and sugar over--</l>
               <l>like a syrupy sweet?</l>
               <l>Maybe it just sags</l>
               <l>like a heavy load.</l>
               <l>Or does it explode?</l>
             </lg>
            </div>
        
      </body>
